text: Broad Street National Bank is located in Trenton, Mercer County, New Jersey, United States. The building was built in 1900 and added to the National Register of Historic Places on January 17, 2008. ==See also== *National Register of Historic Places listings in Mercer County, New Jersey ==References== Category:Commercial buildings on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:Commercial buildings completed in 1900 Category:Buildings and structures in Trenton, New Jersey Category:National Register of Historic Places in Trenton, New Jersey Category:New Jersey Register of Historic Places Category:Skyscrapers in New Jersey Category:Skyscraper office buildings in New Jersey
title: Broad Street National Bank
